default3. defaultEco-friendly Standardsdefault3.1
default              
defaultThe RTPI is concerned that too little attention has been given to the potential for higher standards to be justified and marketed on the basis of the significant user savings achievable. 
default3.2
default              
defaultIn particular there is potential for lenders to incorporate more explicitly the savings as an incentive mechanism into their loan-to-income evaluations for lending.
